01:16:40,800 --> 01:16:44,560
 I kad čuti, ja kužim šta on misli

1166
01:16:44,560 --> 01:16:46,160
 i on zna šta ja mislim,

1167
01:16:46,160 --> 01:16:49,400
 ali ako je nepotrebno, nećemo to izgovoriti.

1168
01:16:49,400 --> 01:16:55,480
 Ali je on također vrlo bitan i važan i uspišan muškarac.

1169
01:16:55,480 --> 01:16:59,000
 Pa, mislim, nećemo biti, nećemo si lagati,

1170
01:16:59,000 --> 01:17:00,980
 ali ženski libido ide na to.

1171
01:17:01,600 --> 01:17:04,560
 Ženski libido ne ide na napuhanog dečka

1172
01:17:04,560 --> 01:17:07,240
 koji ima mišiće i ne znam šta,

1173
01:17:07,240 --> 01:17:08,600
 ima ziro u glavi.

1174
01:17:08,600 --> 01:17:11,020
 Ne, to ne postoji.

1175
01:17:11,020 --> 01:17:12,580
 Ženski libido ide,

1176
01:17:12,580 --> 01:17:14,020
 ona je iz pećine,

1177
01:17:14,020 --> 01:17:15,520
 ko donese veći plijen,

1178
01:17:15,520 --> 01:17:18,080
 odnosno sad govorim o mentalnoj strani.

1179
01:17:18,080 --> 01:17:20,140
 Mene je strašno mentalna strana,

1180
01:17:20,140 --> 01:17:22,080
 znači može uzbuditi.

1181
01:17:22,080 --> 01:17:23,320
 kad je neko pametan.

1182
01:17:23,320 --> 01:17:26,360
 E, onda kad je neko još pametniji od mene,

1183
01:17:26,360 --> 01:17:27,700
 onda je to, ono,

1184
01:17:27,700 --> 01:17:28,780
 orgazam.

1185
01:17:28,780 --> 01:17:31,120
 Ali, ovaj,

1186
01:17:31,120 --> 01:17:36,780
 mislim da smo mi žene tu daleko više evoluirale

1187
01:17:36,780 --> 01:17:37,960
 po tom pitanju.

1188
01:17:40,460 --> 01:17:43,420
 meni nikad nikog,

1189
01:17:43,420 --> 01:17:46,860
 za koga smatram da baš nije previše pametan,

1190
01:17:46,860 --> 01:17:50,620
 da ne znam koliko je bogat ili šta vozi ili nešto.

1191
01:17:50,620 --> 01:17:52,060
 Mislim, mogu se sam smijati,

1192
01:17:52,060 --> 01:17:55,240
 ne otići spavat s takvim čovjekom

1193
01:17:55,240 --> 01:17:57,380
 ili biti uzbuđena s takvim čovjekom.

1194
01:17:57,380 --> 01:17:58,460
 To, to, to,

1195
01:17:58,460 --> 01:17:59,380
 to, to,

1196
01:17:59,380 --> 01:18:01,440
 kad sam bila najmlađa mi nije bilo.

1197
01:18:01,440 --> 01:18:04,080
 Znači, ženski libido u većini

1198
01:18:04,080 --> 01:18:05,760
 ide na uspješne muškarce.

1199
01:18:05,760 --> 01:18:08,220
 Da li je to sad pamet ili je to materialno,

1200
01:18:08,220 --> 01:18:09,900
 to je sad druga stvar,

1201
01:18:09,900 --> 01:18:11,500
 ovisno ženi šta želi

1202
01:18:11,500 --> 01:18:12,940
 i na kojem je nivou,

1203
01:18:12,940 --> 01:18:15,460
 ali mislim da kod

1204
01:18:15,460 --> 01:18:17,320
 pametnih žena,

1205
01:18:17,320 --> 01:18:19,000
 pametni muškarci prolaze.

1206
01:18:19,000 --> 01:18:20,520
 Znači,

1207
01:18:20,520 --> 01:18:23,300
 Ivica je najpoznatiji hrvatski vinar,

1208
01:18:23,300 --> 01:18:23,740
 je li tako?

1209
01:18:23,740 --> 01:18:24,440
 Među najpoznatiji.

1210
01:18:24,440 --> 01:18:25,440
 Među najpoznatiji.

1211
01:18:25,440 --> 01:18:30,680
 On ne voli su velike hvaljenja i tako.

1212
01:18:30,680 --> 01:18:32,880
 Ali je,

1213
01:18:32,880 --> 01:18:36,100
 on je, on je jak i jak elanac

1214
01:18:36,100 --> 01:18:39,300
 u Istri karika

1215
01:18:39,300 --> 01:18:41,100
 tog postizanja

1216
01:18:41,100 --> 01:18:44,380
 toliko velike vrijednosti Malvazije

1217
01:18:44,380 --> 01:18:48,940
 i samog tog organizirane,

1218
01:18:48,940 --> 01:18:51,060
 organizirane, znači,

1219
01:18:51,060 --> 01:18:53,640
 vinarske regije

1220
01:18:53,640 --> 01:18:56,200
 koja je izuzetno uspješna

1221
01:18:56,200 --> 01:18:57,880
 i najuspješnija u Hrvatskoj.

1222
01:18:57,880 --> 01:19:02,620
 Tako da njegova ta obsesija

1223
01:19:02,620 --> 01:19:04,720
 svojim vinogradima

1224
01:19:04,720 --> 01:19:06,320
 i svojim vinom

1225
01:19:06,320 --> 01:19:08,740
 je meni strašno uzbudljiva.

1226
01:19:09,320 --> 01:19:11,840
 ja ponekad znam vi kad tebi je vinograd

1227
01:19:11,840 --> 01:19:15,840
 najbitnije cvjeti, ti ne bi primijetio da ja nestanem,

1228
01:19:15,840 --> 01:19:17,340
 ja u biti obožavam to.

1229
01:19:17,760 --> 01:19:19,100
 zato što nije na meni.

1230
01:19:19,100 --> 01:19:34,200
 Ne sisava iz mene nekakvu, nego ima svoju obsesiju, ima svoju strast i znam da stvarno to živi i to mi je nešto što mi jako puno znači.

1231
01:19:34,320 --> 01:19:38,640
 Ali Djurjice, ovi Iron Mani su zapravo vaši Iron Mani.

1232
01:19:38,640 --> 01:19:39,920
 Da, on je u svakom,

1233
01:19:39,920 --> 01:19:44,060
 bili mogla bez njega, bez njegove organizacije, logistike.

1234
01:19:44,060 --> 01:19:44,740
 Bi.

1235
01:19:44,740 --> 01:19:46,540
 Bi.

1236
01:19:46,540 --> 01:19:47,740
 Sjajno.

1237
01:19:47,740 --> 01:19:49,960
 Ja mislim,

1238
01:19:49,960 --> 01:19:52,500
 on je zaista

1239
01:19:52,500 --> 01:19:54,840
 jedna podrška

1240
01:19:54,840 --> 01:19:56,560
 koja je, vjerovatno

1241
01:19:56,560 --> 01:19:58,480
 zavijedila sam ju da ju imam.

1242
01:19:58,480 --> 01:20:00,400
 Kad neko kažu tako,

1243
01:20:00,400 --> 01:20:01,760
 dosta ti, recimo,

1244
01:20:01,760 --> 01:20:04,500
 zavidni ljudi, žene, muškarci,

1245
01:20:04,500 --> 01:20:06,080
 pa lako njoj kad ima njega.

1246
01:20:06,080 --> 01:20:08,000
 Pa ko? Zašto ti nemaš?

1247
01:20:08,280 --> 01:20:09,580
 Zato što nisi zavrijedila

1248
01:20:09,580 --> 01:20:11,740
 ili zavrijedio da imaš nekog takvog.

1249
01:20:11,740 --> 01:20:13,800
 Hajde, zavrijedi.

1250
01:20:13,800 --> 01:20:14,700
 Budi iskren.

1251
01:20:14,700 --> 01:20:20,700
 Ne, ljudi uvijek traže nekakve razloge zašto je neko.

1252
01:20:20,700 --> 01:20:22,420
 To što se ja dižem,

1253
01:20:22,420 --> 01:20:24,500
 u četiri ujutro idem na trening,

1254
01:20:24,500 --> 01:20:26,800
 da sam već u osam doma,

1255
01:20:26,800 --> 01:20:27,780
 kad se svi bude,

1256
01:20:27,780 --> 01:20:29,360
 napravim smuti,

1257
01:20:29,360 --> 01:20:32,280
 popijemo kavu, obožavam to i odem u optiku.

1258
01:20:32,280 --> 01:20:34,400
 To nikom nije bitno.

1259
01:20:34,400 --> 01:20:36,760
 Znači što svaki dan treniram,

1260
01:20:37,920 --> 01:20:41,140
 svaki dan jebeno plivam u tom bazenu,

1261
01:20:41,140 --> 01:20:42,840
 pre slanom, pre toplom,

1262
01:20:42,840 --> 01:20:45,700
 da radim tehniku od koje nema pomoći,

1263
01:20:45,700 --> 01:20:47,380
 jer sam naučila u 49. godini

1264
01:20:47,380 --> 01:20:49,160
 plivat kraul, pa uvijek

1265
01:20:49,160 --> 01:20:51,380
 napravim u trci onako kakav mi je dan,

1266
01:20:51,380 --> 01:20:53,220
 a ne koliko sam vježbala,

1267
01:20:53,220 --> 01:20:55,260
 napravim po 7 kilometara tjedno.

1268
01:20:56,260 --> 01:20:59,040
 i uporna sam u tome i neću odustati.

1269
01:20:59,320 --> 01:21:00,700
 Znači nije važan talent,

1270
01:21:00,700 --> 01:21:02,380
 nego disciplina i upornosti.

1271
01:21:02,380 --> 01:21:03,540
 Jako, jako.

1272
01:21:03,540 --> 01:21:04,420
 Najviše.

1273
01:21:04,420 --> 01:21:07,980
 Mislim, ništa nije važnije

1274
01:21:07,980 --> 01:21:10,660
 u triatlonu od upornosti.

1275
01:21:10,660 --> 01:21:13,380
 I ono između ostalog,

1276
01:21:13,380 --> 01:21:16,480
 što sam najviše ponosna na sebe

1277
01:21:16,480 --> 01:21:18,740
 u mom sportskom životu,

1278
01:21:18,740 --> 01:21:20,760
 su moji treninzi.

1279
01:21:21,700 --> 01:21:23,440
 Znači, u ovih 11 godina

1280
01:21:23,440 --> 01:21:25,360
 ja svaki dan treniram.

1281
01:21:25,360 --> 01:21:28,000
 To je strašno.

1282
01:21:28,000 --> 01:21:30,020
 To su strašni kilometri.

1283
01:21:30,020 --> 01:21:32,800
 Ali ja 11 godina se trudim

1284
01:21:32,800 --> 01:21:34,160
 da budim tu gdje jesam.

1285
01:21:34,160 --> 01:21:36,700
 Ni samo zbog rezultata,

1286
01:21:36,700 --> 01:21:38,500
 nego da sebi dokažem

1287
01:21:38,500 --> 01:21:39,480
 da ja to mogu.

1288
01:21:39,480 --> 01:21:41,540
 A obužavam to.

1289
01:21:41,540 --> 01:21:44,400
 Mislim, ja ne mogu zamisliti.

1290
01:21:44,400 --> 01:21:45,920
 To je čista ovisnost.

1291
01:21:45,920 --> 01:21:48,300
 Znači, ja kažem trčanje je laka droga,

1292
01:21:48,300 --> 01:21:50,420
 a triatlon je teška droga.

1293
01:21:50,420 --> 01:21:51,520
 Tako da je to,

1294
01:21:51,520 --> 01:21:53,040
 to je razlika.

1295
01:21:53,040 --> 01:21:55,580
 Ja sam ovisna o tome.

1296
01:21:55,580 --> 01:21:56,900
 Znači, mi kad god putujemo,

1297
01:21:56,900 --> 01:21:58,640
 vozimo biciklu sa mnom,

1298
01:21:58,640 --> 01:22:00,680
 ja moram napraviti.

1299
01:22:00,680 --> 01:22:02,760
 Onda on kad rezervira smješta

1300
01:22:02,760 --> 01:22:04,760
 i gleda da ima bazen za plivanje.

1301
01:22:04,760 --> 01:22:06,500
 Onda ovo, ono je znači.

1302
01:22:06,500 --> 01:22:08,160
 I on me uvijek podržava.

1303
01:22:08,160 --> 01:22:09,220
 Nikad nije rekao,

1304
01:22:09,220 --> 01:22:11,580
 joj, ili ako imamo nešto dogovoreno,

1305
01:22:11,580 --> 01:22:12,520
 ja kažem, ne mogu sutra,

1306
01:22:12,520 --> 01:22:13,620
 imam duga čak trening,

1307
01:22:13,620 --> 01:22:14,520
 goditi sam,

1308
01:22:14,520 --> 01:22:16,120
 a daj obeća sa načem,

1309
01:22:16,120 --> 01:22:16,940
 onda od skupa,

1310
01:22:16,940 --> 01:22:18,620
 masu puta kažem,

1311
01:22:18,620 --> 01:22:19,340
 žao mi je.

1312
01:22:19,340 --> 01:22:20,780
 i on ode sam

1313
01:22:20,780 --> 01:22:22,960
 i znam da mu je neugodno,

1314
01:22:22,960 --> 01:22:25,020
 da su svi došli u parovima,

1315
01:22:25,020 --> 01:22:26,760
 da je on sad sam tamo.

1316
01:22:26,760 --> 01:22:28,100
 Ali on me razumije,

1317
01:22:28,100 --> 01:22:29,740
 ali on me iskreno razumije.

1318
01:22:29,740 --> 01:22:31,640
 Iskreno me razumije,

1319
01:22:31,640 --> 01:22:32,940
 koliko god je muškarac,

1320
01:22:32,940 --> 01:22:35,740
 ali je različit muškarac.

1321
01:22:35,800 --> 01:22:37,720
 muškarac koji čini razliku.

1322
01:22:37,720 --> 01:22:42,620
 I jako sam sretna što smo se tako slučajno,

1323
01:22:42,620 --> 01:22:44,480
 na Vinistri smo se upoznali

1324
01:22:44,480 --> 01:22:46,440
 i kako smo se upoznali,

1325
01:22:46,440 --> 01:22:47,540
 nismo se razvojili,

1326
01:22:47,540 --> 01:22:48,260
 da slavu se.

1327
01:22:48,260 --> 01:22:51,280
 Koliko ti znači njegova podrška?

1328
01:22:51,400 --> 01:22:51,860
 sjećam se,

1329
01:22:51,860 --> 01:22:53,340
 u knjizi si opisala trenutak,

1330
01:22:53,340 --> 01:22:55,180
 prvi kad neće kaš se da,

1331
01:22:55,180 --> 01:22:57,280
 kad misleš da li možeš ti triatlon,

1332
01:22:57,280 --> 01:22:57,580
 ma ne,

1333
01:22:57,580 --> 01:22:58,660
 nećeš ti triatlon.

1334
01:22:58,660 --> 01:23:00,520
 Prvi put kad si...

1335
01:23:00,520 --> 01:23:02,060
 Da, u poreču kad je bilo,

1336
01:23:02,060 --> 01:23:03,660
 kad sam htjela duatlon odraditi,

1337
01:23:03,660 --> 01:23:04,660
 privanje i trčanje.

1338
01:23:04,660 --> 01:23:06,440
 Ti si htjela duatlon i on je rekao...

1339
01:23:06,440 --> 01:23:07,300
 Pa ne znam od me,

1340
01:23:07,300 --> 01:23:09,700
 on me je nagovorio doslovce na triatlon.

1341
01:23:09,700 --> 01:23:11,780
 Da, on je rekao,

1342
01:23:11,780 --> 01:23:13,160
 kupit ćemo svu oprenu,

1343
01:23:13,160 --> 01:23:14,320
 nećeš raditi duatlon,

1344
01:23:14,320 --> 01:23:15,360
 radit ćeš triatlon.

1345
01:23:15,360 --> 01:23:16,060
 Možeš ti to?

1346
01:23:16,060 --> 01:23:16,860
 Možeš ti to.

1347
01:23:16,860 --> 01:23:20,100
 U 15 dana se spremi za dugi triatlon.

1348
01:23:20,100 --> 01:23:22,980
 110 kilometara je bilo.

1349
01:23:22,980 --> 01:23:24,700
 To nijedan luđaka.

1350
01:23:24,700 --> 01:23:25,140
 Zašto?

1351
01:23:25,140 --> 01:23:27,240
 Zato što ja imam poremeća jedan,

1352
01:23:27,240 --> 01:23:28,480
 ja ne znam lijevo desno

1353
01:23:28,480 --> 01:23:31,420
 i ne mogu vizualizirati kvadrate,

1354
01:23:31,420 --> 01:23:32,300
 ni kilometre.

1355
01:23:32,300 --> 01:23:33,860
 Ja sam ti ko ono,

1356
01:23:33,860 --> 01:23:36,320
 šta cigo zna šta je 300 kila,

1357
01:23:36,320 --> 01:23:37,120
 uzme i nosi.

1358
01:23:37,120 --> 01:23:38,880
 Tako sam ja ušla i u maraton,

1359
01:23:38,880 --> 01:23:40,220
 i u triatlon

1360
01:23:40,220 --> 01:23:43,500
 i ne razmišljam o kilometrima,

1361
01:23:43,500 --> 01:23:44,900
 o tome što mene čeka,

1362
01:23:44,900 --> 01:23:47,420
 nego samo krenem.

1363
01:23:47,420 --> 01:23:49,240
 Pa dok le stignem.

1364
01:23:49,240 --> 01:23:50,260
 Ali sam toliko uporna

1365
01:23:50,260 --> 01:23:51,340
 da uvijek dođem do cilja.

1366
01:23:51,340 --> 01:23:54,320
 Primijetila sam da puno plaćeš.

1367
01:23:54,320 --> 01:23:55,480
 Plaćeš od sreće,

1368
01:23:55,480 --> 01:23:57,420
 plaćeš od tuge,

1369
01:23:57,540 --> 01:23:58,540
 plaćeš stvarno,

1370
01:23:58,540 --> 01:24:00,080
 izražavaš svoje emocije,

1371
01:24:00,080 --> 01:24:00,680
 ne skrivaš ih,

1372
01:24:00,680 --> 01:24:02,420
 nego si baš onako...

1373
01:24:02,420 --> 01:24:03,760
 Pa mislim da je to zbog toga

1374
01:24:03,760 --> 01:24:05,980
 što počinjem živiti to djete u sebi.

1375
01:24:05,980 --> 01:24:08,020
 A djeca ne mogu sakrit plać.

1376
01:24:08,020 --> 01:24:09,860
 I onda...

1377
01:24:09,860 --> 01:24:11,540
 Zašto bi uopće ga trebali sakrit?

1378
01:24:11,540 --> 01:24:13,040
 Pa zato što smo tako odgojeni.

1379
01:24:13,040 --> 01:24:14,380
 Nije lijepo da budeš ono,

1380
01:24:14,380 --> 01:24:15,920
 pička stalno plaćeš,

1381
01:24:16,000 --> 01:24:16,140
 jel?

1382
01:24:16,140 --> 01:24:18,360
 A tako mi je jedan

1383
01:24:18,360 --> 01:24:21,400
 drag i prijatelj isto,

1384
01:24:21,400 --> 01:24:22,220
 ovaj,

1385
01:24:22,220 --> 01:24:23,260
 novinar,

1386
01:24:23,260 --> 01:24:24,160
 koji mi je rekao je,

1387
01:24:24,160 --> 01:24:25,560
 ja sam prođite o knjigu,

1388
01:24:25,560 --> 01:24:26,260
 genijalna.

1389
01:24:26,260 --> 01:24:27,980
 Stvarno sam mislio ono,

1390
01:24:27,980 --> 01:24:29,640
 da stalno,

1391
01:24:29,640 --> 01:24:30,280
 ovaj,

1392
01:24:31,460 --> 01:24:32,260
 cmizriš,

1393
01:24:32,260 --> 01:24:33,180
 ali sad sam shvatio

1394
01:24:33,180 --> 01:24:34,780
 da ovaj,

1395
01:24:34,780 --> 01:24:35,320
 da,

1396
01:24:35,320 --> 01:24:35,820
 da,

1397
01:24:35,820 --> 01:24:36,760
 da je to

1398
01:24:36,760 --> 01:24:39,420
 stvarno ima razloga

1399
01:24:39,420 --> 01:24:40,700
 i da si ti takva osoba.

1400
01:24:40,700 --> 01:24:41,920
 Ja koliko god sam snažna

1401
01:24:41,920 --> 01:24:42,960
 i potući ću se sa

1402
01:24:42,960 --> 01:24:45,200
 duplo većim od sebe,

1403
01:24:45,200 --> 01:24:46,740
 ako osjetim neku nepravdu,

1404
01:24:46,740 --> 01:24:48,040
 ja odmah idem.

1405
01:24:48,040 --> 01:24:50,880
 A isto tako ću se rasplakat

1406
01:24:50,880 --> 01:24:52,080
 na malom

1407
01:24:52,080 --> 01:24:53,840
 mače tamo

1408
01:24:53,840 --> 01:24:54,160
 ili,

1409
01:24:54,160 --> 01:24:55,880
 ili ja kad vozim biciklu,

1410
01:24:55,880 --> 01:24:56,480
 ja stanem,

